hardirqs last  enabled at (47913): [<c0098824>] console_unlock+0x46c/0x680
hardirqs last disabled at (47922): [<c0098470>] console_unlock+0xb8/0x680
softirqs last  enabled at (47754): [<c000a484>] __do_softirq+0x344/0x540
